傷財，認為政府須交代用了多少公帑，「你唔封關，驗幾多都冇用啦！」"},{"pid":"ddad31e1d20aae55f44574c527be14569fde1654","tid":2201655,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"佢真係好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬼佬何柏良咁"}]}